headline: ABBV Q3 Deep Dive: Immunology Growth and Pipeline Expansion Offset Margin Pressure
summary: Pharmaceutical company AbbVie (NYSE:ABBV) reported Q3 CY2025 results exceeding the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 9.1% year on year to $15.78 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.86 per share was 4.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
